I can see this.I learned from a friend to use Zod to check for process.env. I refined it a bit  and got:```const EnvSchema = z.object({  NODE_ENV: z.enum(['development', 'production', 'staging']),

  DATABASE_URL: z.string(),

  POSTHOG_KEY: z.string(),

});export type AlertDownEnv = z.infer<typeof EnvSchema>;export function getEnvironments(env: Record<string, string>): AlertDownEnv {
